        </div>
        <div class="pcard-body">
          <span class="pcard-brand">BENEFIBER</span>
          <h3 class="pcard-name">Prebiotic Fiber Gummies</h3>
          <div class="pcard-stars">
            <span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;</span>
            <span class="rating-val">4.6</span>
            <span class="review-ct">(18,456 reviews)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-specs">
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Fiber Type</strong><span>Prebiotic Fiber (Wheat Dextrin)</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Dose</strong><span>3g fiber per serving</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Servings</strong><span>60 per container</span></div>
            <div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Testing</strong><span>Third-party tested &#10003;</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-price">
            <span class="price">$16.99</span>
            <span class="per-serv">$0.28/serving</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-pros-cons">
            <div class="pcard-pros">
              <h4>Pros</h4>
