          </div>
          <div class="pcard-price">
            <span class="price">$15.99</span>
            <span class="per-serv">$0.27/serving</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pcard-pros-cons">
            <div class="pcard-pros">
              <h4>Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>#1 doctor-recommended fiber brand in the United States</li>
                <li>5g fiber per serving — tied for highest dose on this list</li>
                <li>Decades of clinical evidence behind the Metamucil name</li>
